<body lang=3D"EN-NZ" link=3D"blue" vlink=3D"purple" style=3D"word-wrap:brea=
k-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Kia ora R=
afaella,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Thank you=
 for your detailed email and for raising these concerns. I want to acknowle=
dge the stress and frustration this situation has caused, especially given =
the circumstances you're already navigating
 following the fire. We take your concerns seriously and are committed to a=
ddressing them thoroughly and respectfully.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">A) Securi=
ty / Containment<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We sincer=
ely apologise for the oversight regarding the link access. We have now:<o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0cm" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1"><span style=3D"ms=
o-fareast-language:EN-US">Disabled the current ShareFile link.<o:p></o:p></=
span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1"><span s=
tyle=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Initiated a reissue of access that is r=
estricted and tied solely to your email address.
<a href=3D"https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sb3797728cdc745088741e36a60cdfbe=
1">https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sb3797728cdc745088741e36a60cdfbe1</a>
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 =
lfo1"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">A full audit log from Shar=
eFile, including activity, and access events. This has been uploaded to you=
r file.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We have u=
sed the Privacy Commissioners =E2=80=9CNotifyUs=E2=80=9D tool as requested =
on 15 September to review whether this incident meets the threshold for a n=
otifiable privacy breach under the Privacy Act. We confirm
 the outcome of that assessment return being unlikely event, due to that To=
wer can see who has access to the link and the link has only been shared to=
 yourself. The report is also included in your file in the link.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">B) Substa=
ntive Privacy Act Response<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We acknow=
ledge your original request and the legal entitlements under IPP6 of the Pr=
ivacy Act 2020. We are now conducting a fresh, enterprise-wide search acros=
s all relevant systems and third-party
 providers to ensure completeness. This includes:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0cm" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2"><span style=3D"ms=
o-fareast-language:EN-US">Internal communications (email, IM, call logs, tr=
anscripts)<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:=
l2 level1 lfo2"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Third-party inst=
ructions and correspondence<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" s=
tyle=3D"mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"=
>Site media and technical reports<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNor=
mal" style=3D"mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:=
EN-US">ShareFile configuration and access logs. Already included.<o:p></o:p=
></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">However, =
we won=E2=80=99t be providing a document index for this privacy request, as=
 creating one would be a significant administrative task and isn=E2=80=99t =
something we=E2=80=99re required to do under the Privacy Act.
 The Act requires us to provide access to existing personal information, bu=
t not to create new documents or indexes. We=E2=80=99d also like to note th=
at if a request is particularly detailed or requires a lot of extra work to=
 process, we are entitled to charge a reasonable
 fee to cover the administrative costs involved.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Grounds f=
or any redactions or withholdings, however, some documents have been withhe=
ld or redacted because they contain the personal information of other indiv=
iduals, which we are legally required
 to protect under the Privacy Act. Additionally, certain documents include =
commercially sensitive information=E2=80=94such as contractor pricing or in=
ternal business processes, that cannot be disclosed. We understand this may=
 be disappointing, and we=E2=80=99re committed to
 being as transparent as possible within those legal and commercial boundar=
ies. This said, we will provide more detail where we can on the specific re=
dactions.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">C) Record=
s Preservation<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We confir=
m that all records relating to your claims are being preserved until both m=
atters are fully resolved and all requested documentation has been provided.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We apprec=
iate your patience and your clear articulation of the issues. Please know t=
hat we are treating this with urgency and care, and we are committed to res=
olving it directly with you.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Warm rega=
rds<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<div>
