Classification: Sensitive<br>
</p>
<div style=3D"border:none;border-top:solid #E1E1E1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm =
0cm 0cm">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;fo=
nt-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">From:</span></b><span lang=3D"EN-=
US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"> =
Raffaella del Prete &lt;raffaellanz@icloud.com&gt;
<br>
<b>Sent:</b> Thursday, 18 September 2025 6:42 pm<br>
<b>To:</b> Privacy &lt;Privacy@tower.co.nz&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: Privacy Request<br>
<b>Importance:</b> High<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-line-height-alt:.75pt"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white">Kia ora Privacy Team, Thanks for checking in. I=
 can access the link; however, it is not identity-restricted. As a test, I =
could open the folder using a different,
 unknown email address simply by entering a name and passing reCAPTCHA. I=
=E2=80=99ve saved<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-line-height-alt:.75pt"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Kia ora Privacy Team,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thanks for checking in. I can access the link; howev=
er, it is not identity-restricted. As a test, I could open the folder using=
 a different, unknown email address simply by entering a name and passing r=
eCAPTCHA. I=E2=80=99ve saved screenshots.
 Please treat this as a security issue.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">For clarity, on 1 July 2025 I requested a full copy =
of my file for both claims (C90306048 and C90306256), =E2=80=9Cincluding al=
l internal notes, reports, third-party correspondence, scopes, assessments,=
 emails, and any other material Tower holds
 in relation to these claims.=E2=80=9D<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Legal effect: Under IPP6 Privacy Act 2020, I=E2=80=
=99m entitled to access my personal information. =E2=80=9CIncluding=E2=80=
=9D is non-exhaustive, covering all formats and systems (e.g., email, IM/Te=
ams/Slack, call recordings/transcripts, SMS, photos/video, test
 results, and native costing spreadsheets). It also extends to information =
held for Tower by its agents/contractors. If anything is withheld or redact=
ed, please identify the specific ground(s).<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Fair Insurance Code: As a signatory, Tower commits t=
o handling claims and complaints honestly, fairly, transparently, and in a =
timely way, with clear communication about what you will do and when. The i=
nsecure link, incomplete response,
 and broad redactions to date don=E2=80=99t feel consistent with those comm=
itments.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I also want to note the human impact. I=E2=80=99m al=
ready dealing with the aftermath of the fire; the insecure link, incomplete=
 response, and redactions have added avoidable stress and time burden.<o:p>=
</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">REQUESTS AND TIMEFRAMES<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">A) Security / containment =E2=80=93 by 5:00pm NZT, T=
hursday 25 September 2025<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-=
alt:auto;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3">
Revoke/disable the current link(s) and re-issue recipient-specific access t=
ied solely to my email (no public link).<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNor=
mal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l=
3 level1 lfo3">
Provide ShareFile audit logs (link creation, permissions, and all access ev=
ents: timestamp, user/email, IP, action).<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNo=
rmal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:=
l3 level1 lfo3">
Confirm the containment steps taken and whether a notifiable privacy breach=
 assessment was made; if notified, please provide the OPC reference number;=
 if not, please provide your serious-harm assessment.<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">B) Substantive Privacy Act response =E2=80=93 by 5:0=
0pm NZT, Thursday 25 September 2025<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please conduct a fresh, enterprise-wide search and p=
rovide the complete files across all systems and agents/contractors for bot=
h claims, including (non-exhaustive):<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-=
alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4">
Claim diary/notes and task logs (full chronology).<o:p></o:p></li><li class=
=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;=
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4">
Internal communications: emails and IM (e.g., Teams/Slack).<o:p></o:p></li>=
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-=
alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4">
Call recordings/transcripts for all calls with me (inbound/outbound), any v=
ideo calls, and voicemail.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"=
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4">
SMS/texts and chat messages with me.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal"=
 style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 le=
vel1 lfo4">
Instructions to/from assessors and contractors, all quotes/scopes/variation=
s, and native costing files/spreadsheets used to build any scope/SOW.<o:p><=
/o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-marg=
in-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4">
Site media: all photos and videos.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" s=
tyle=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 leve=
l1 lfo4">
Testing/technical reports: moisture logs; soot/smoke/odour assessments; HVA=
C/duct contamination; asbestos sampling/clearances; electrical, gas, and en=
gineering reports/results.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"=
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4">
Third-party correspondence relating to my claims.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=
=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;=
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4">
ShareFile configuration and access/audit logs for links used to provide my =
data.<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please also provide a document index (date, author, =
short description, and system/location) so I can verify completeness. For e=
ach redaction/withholding, identify the specific ground(s).<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">To assist completeness, please include a brief searc=
h methodology (systems searched, date ranges, search terms, and which third=
 parties were asked to supply records). If any category does not exist, ple=
ase state that expressly.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">C) Records preservation (effective immediately)<o:p>=
</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please preserve all records relating to my claims =
=E2=80=94 until both claims have been fully settled and all requested docum=
entation has been provided. This includes contractor files, access logs and=
 backups. Kindly confirm &nbsp;that any automatic
 deletion settings have been paused for the relevant mailboxes, systems and=
 backups.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">For reference, the current folder contains only six =
documents (which I have consolidated in teh attached file) , which is plain=
ly incomplete for a full file response. I=E2=80=99m keen to resolve this di=
rectly and will review whatever you provide
 promptly.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
